description: Dash is pretending to be a butler to spy on the guests. Maybe one of them has the information you're looking for.

puzzles.introduction: A good butler is always on the move.

hints.description: Set the Move To state to 20 cm in the forward direction. Link the state with an Auto cue.

puzzles.description: After moving forward, make Dash randomly choose to spin to -45 degrees. Then make Dash automatically move forward again.
puzzles.introduction: Sometimes a butler has to spin right...

hints.description: Edit the Spin To state to make Dash turn -45 degrees.

puzzles.description: After moving forward, make Dash randomly choose to spin to 45 degrees. Then make Dash automatically move forward again.
puzzles.introduction: And sometimes a butler has to spin left.

hints.description: Edit the new Spin To state to make Dash turn 45 degrees. Link the state with a Random Link cue and an Auto cue.

puzzles.description: After moving forward, make Dash randomly choose to spin to 180 degrees. Then make Dash automatically move forward again.
puzzles.introduction: And a butler needs to be able to do a 180 when necessary!

hints.description: Edit the new Spin To state to make Dash turn 180 degrees. Link the state with a Random Link cue and an Auto cue.

puzzles.description: While moving forward, make Dash smile if an obstacle is seen in front.
puzzles.introduction: A good butler needs a good smile.

hints.description: Link the Eye Ring with an Obstacle Seen cue. Set the cue to only detect obstacles that are very close to the front of Dash.

puzzles.description: Edit the custom sound to make Butler Dash offer some food.
puzzles.introduction: Hi there. Would you like some cheese?

hints.description: Record your own message in the Custom Sound to make Dash offer some food.

puzzles.description: After smiling, make Dash randomly choose to play a new custom sound that offers something to eat or drink.
puzzles.introduction: Greetings, ma'am! Would you like a marshmallow?

hints.description: Record your own message in the new Custom Sound to make Dash offer something to eat or drink. Link the Eye Ring to the sound with a Random Link cue.

puzzles.description: After smiling, make Dash randomly choose to play another custom sound that offers a different kind of food or drink. Then make Dash automatically move forward again.
puzzles.introduction: Excuse me sir, would you like a potato?

hints.description: Record your own message in the new Custom Sound. Link the Eye Ring to the sound with a Random Link cue. Link the sound to the Move To state with an Auto cue.
